description:
An Electron app for uploading diabetes device data to Tidepool's backend

Tidepool Uploader is a universal uploader app that allows you to retrieve data from supported devices, including every brand of insulin pump and continuous glucose monitor (CGM) on the US market and a wide variety of blood glucose meters and diabetes apps.
What's Changed
- Update ReliOn Prime upload instructions and fix Windows code signing (UPLOAD-1480, UPLOAD-1486) by @gniezen in https://github.com/tidepool-org/uploader/pull/1694
- Fix for ReliOn Premier Classic progress bar (UPLOAD-1387) by @gniezen in https://github.com/tidepool-org/uploader/pull/1701
- Store Tandem pump shutdown events so that they can be displayed in Tidepool Web (UPLOAD-1461) by @gniezen in https://github.com/tidepool-org/uploader/pull/1690
- Add error message that Omnipod 5 PDM is unsupported (UPLOAD-1464) by @gniezen in https://github.com/tidepool-org/uploader/pull/1692
- Fixing regression in timestamps for Bluetooth uploads (UPLOAD-1495) by @gniezen in https://github.com/tidepool-org/uploader/pull/1697
- Handle Tandem Control-IQ+ temp basals (UPLOAD-1494) by @gniezen in https://github.com/tidepool-org/uploader/pull/1696
Full Changelog: https://github.com/tidepool-org/uploader/compare/v2.62.0...v2.63.0
